Say '''Bamban''' et kumadwa ya klase baley ed luyag na [[Tarlac]], [[Pilipinas]]. <br>  
Unong ed 2010 Census, say papulasyon to et 62,413 totoo. Walay kabaleg tan sukat to ya 251.98 sq. km. Sikato et walad kumatlo  distrito. Say zip code to et 2317.

